room_title: Escape room "Gold Rush" by The Escape Game Nashville in Nashville
review: We love The Escape Game Nashville, but wow, Gold Rush was AMAZING!!! We had such a fun time! Best game so far!!!! Can't wait to see what games you guys come up with next!!

room_title: Escape room "Gold Rush" by The Escape Game Nashville in Nashville
review: Absolutely LOVED the experience! Our team of 3 tried to escape Gold Rush and ALMOST made it. You can't go anywhere else and do something like this. I will be back.

room_title: Escape room "Gold Rush" by The Escape Game Nashville in Nashville
review: Oh my gosh! What a great way to celebrate my 30th birthday; being a kid again! I won't give anything away, but Gold Rush was awesome! Can't wait to go back.

room_title: Escape room "Gold Rush" by The Escape Game Nashville in Nashville
review: Had so much fun!! Absolutely one of the best experiences we've ever had. We all want to do them all now. Can't wait to do it again!

room_title: Escape room "Gold Rush" by The Escape Game Nashville in Nashville
review: This was one of the most fun things I've ever done!!!! It was extremely challenging and I would think most everyone would enjoy it. We escaped with 1 min 15 seconds left and were jumping around in celebration.

room_title: Escape room "Gold Rush" by The Escape Game Nashville in Nashville
review: We played the Underground Playground with 7 people, made it out with 10 minutes to spare and didn't use any of our clues!! (I don't count the one they charged us with because we had the thing, and lost it at the very end of the game.) Our group had so much fun solving puzzles and working together. We definitely felt more accomplished than we would have if we had stayed at the bar for another hour ;] I highly recommend this activity for people who like puzzles, trying new things, and building great teams/realtionships!
